Detailed Description

cvmx_pcs::_sgm::_an_adv_reg

SGMII AN Advertisement Register (sent out as tx_config_reg) NOTE: The SGMII AN Advertisement Register above will be sent during Auto Negotiation if the MAC_PHY mode bit in misc_ctl_reg is set (1=PHY mode). If the bit is not set (0=MAC mode), the tx_config_reg[14] becomes ACK bit and [0] is always 1. All other bits in tx_config_reg sent will be 0. The PHY dictates the Auto Negotiation results.
